         MACRO
&NAME    X5ERRL &A,&B,&C
.*       MACRO GENERATES A CALL TO THE PHASE 5 ERROR LOGGING
.*       ROUTINE X51 WITH THE ERROR NUMBER AS A PARAMETER
&NAME    JCALL LOGERR
         DC    AL1(SEV&A,ERR&A,&B,0)        (SEVERITY,ERROR NO.,FLAG,0)
         AIF   ('&C' EQ '').A100
         B     &C                       RECOVER OR ABORT RECORD
.A100    ANOP
         MEND
